NEW Sketchpad Soundscapes Sketchpad: draw or paint your heart s desires right inside your journal along with your existing text photos videos and voice notes. Soundscapes: play relaxing background music bird chirping raindrops fire crackling and more to get into the right headspace while journaling. Many improvements throughout including performance upgrades and design tweaks. Many bug fixes including bugs in the widget. More template options.

We fixed bugs and added improvements to your best friend: Turtle! If only we could fix bugs in our human friends... Enjoy! Previous Update Introducing Turtle v2 This new version blends breathtaking design and technical sophistication to provide you with a powerful journaling experience. New Notepad The redesigned notepad enables you to express yourself with words photos videos and audio. Format color highlight font weight size. Insert photos videos audio directly into the text editor. Delete media with a simple backspace. Your work is automatically saved while you edit. Journal Covers Add wallpaper to personalize your journal. Choose from dozens of beautiful preset options. Import photos from your device. App wide Lock You spoke we listened. Instead of locking individual journals you can now lock the entire app using FaceID TouchID or passcode. Shortcuts Press and hold the app icon to jump right into the notepad. More The app has a fresh new look throughout. New app icon plus new alternate options. View all your drafts in a list. Performance improvements and bug fixes.
